		  <div class="__pf" id="__pf"><div data-pf-type="Body" class="sc-pRgDJ fzXWJx pf-4e258031"><div data-pf-type="Layout" class="pf-3a4e2580"><div data-container="false" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-6d178858" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-6f3a4e25 pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--pf-s-lg:0px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-c16b2ab2" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-f0d4103e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-bfc16b2a">SIZING GUIDE</span></h3></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-976f3a4e" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-85efb6ad pf-r pf-r-align--cm" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-b8a193d1" data-pf-type="Column"><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-ad7edfcc--img-sizing-guide.jpg?v=1595611644 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-ad7edfcc--img-sizing-guide_800x600.jpg?v=1595611644&resized 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-ad7edfcc--img-sizing-guide_400x300.jpg?v=1595611644&resized 400w" alt="sizing guide" class="sc-qZtVr dLIPjF pf-b6ad7edf" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-93d185ef" data-pf-type="Column"><h1 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-2fbc9f09"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-deb42fbc">Find your perfect fit from the comfort of your home. If you don't have time to head to your local jewelry store to get your measurement, then here are three methods to help you figure out your ring size!</span></h1></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-c9314c4b"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-2fd11268 pf-r pf-r-align--cm" style="--pf-s-lg:0px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-902fd112" data-pf-type="Column"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-00368387"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-07902fd1">1. measure an existing ring</span></h6></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-8251e621"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-d8eb10d7 pf-r pf-r-align--ct" style="--pf-s-lg:16px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-7c0124a9" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-24a9f05a" data-pf-type="Column"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-d837f646"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-8679d837">Measure a ring that you (or she) already own! This is the best method to find a ring size if you're planning to surprise her. Simply, just sneak the ring she wears all the time, measure it, place it back before she notices that it's gone!</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-2a9f130c"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-1acc2a9f">How to measure</span></h2><ul style="--text-indent:0; --line-spacing:10px;" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-pcLhl bMMcvF pf-956c5fdf"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-8910c069"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-0f61b535">Save the below ring size chart to your computer.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-c069066c"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-dbdf7b96">Print out the below ring size chart at 25% or set your printer to 'Print As An Entire Image'</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-066ce56a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-173ff3a2">Place the ring over each circle until the ring lines up with the outside of the circle. Make sure that the outside of circle is touching the inside of the ring and you can see the outline of the circle inside the ring.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-e56a956c"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-78da8910">To double check on the fit, take a pencil to trace the inside of the ring against the selected circle. The two circles would match up!</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-d2e6594d"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a29cd2e6">If you measure the internal diameter of the ring (in mm) it should match with the corresponding size in the ring chart.</span></li></ul><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-4d862b45--img-sizing-guide-step-1.jpg?v=1595612833 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-4d862b45--img-sizing-guide-step-1_800x941.jpg?v=1595612833&resized 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-4d862b45--img-sizing-guide-step-1_400x471.jpg?v=1595612833&resized 400w" alt="sizing chart 1" class="sc-qZtVr dLIPjF pf-594d862b" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-f05ad8eb" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-822c95ff"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-694a0e70 pf-r pf-r-align--cm" style="--pf-s-lg:0px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-e2694a0e" data-pf-type="Column"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-d6653598"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-66e2694a">2. measure your finger</span></h6></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-38e8b5bb"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-c47475f1 pf-r pf-r-align--ct" style="--pf-s-lg:16px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-ad7cf8ed" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-7bb7c474" data-pf-type="Column"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-0ddf597e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-db13b61d">Measure a ring with a string or a thin strip paper! This can be easily done and can help find an even accurate fit.</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-597e8da4"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-368bf2cd">How to measure</span></h2><ul style="--text-indent:0; --line-spacing:10px;" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-pcLhl bMMcvF pf-c1887bb7"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-8da40cd4"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-745ddaa2">Cut a long string or piece of paper that's about 6-inches long.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-0cd48fd9"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-330ccd75">Wrap it snugly around the base of your finger, the tighter the better but make sure to not let the string stretch while you're wrapping it around your finger.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-8fd948de"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-63c8d496">Mark the spot where the string or paper meets and measure the distance with a ruler (in mm).</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-48dec188"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-d15c393f">Match your finger measurement (in mm) with the corresponding ring size in the below ring chart.</span></li></ul><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-e4dbad7c--img-sizing-guide-step-2.jpg?v=1595613029 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-e4dbad7c--img-sizing-guide-step-2_800x79.jpg?v=1595613029&resized 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0418/3723/2292/t/2/assets/pf-e4dbad7c--img-sizing-guide-step-2_400x40.jpg?v=1595613029&resized 400w" class="sc-qZtVr dLIPjF pf-393f122f" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-122f0ddf" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-4fe930c9"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-4c58ca5e pf-r pf-r-align--cm" style="--pf-s-lg:0px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-edfd4c58" data-pf-type="Column"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-9119edfd"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-852d9119">3. measure with sewing tape</span></h6></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-5e5ee157"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-831f5028 pf-r pf-r-align--ct" style="--pf-s-lg:16px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-75f1e909" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-7719831f" data-pf-type="Column"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-ce7a54b9"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-8e194ac6">If you happen to own a sewing measuring tape at home, then this is will get the job done most efficiently and accurately!</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-54b9c88b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-cffdf6da">How to measure</span></h2><ul style="--text-indent:0; --line-spacing:10px;" data-pf-type="List" class="sc-pcLhl bMMcvF pf-23467719"><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-c88be12e"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-adeec0d2">Find a flexible, sewing measuring tape with centimeter and/or centimeters on its ruler.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-e12e6257"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-2f0d40a1">Wrap the tape snugly around the base of your finger, not too tight and not too loose. Aim for a snug but comfortable fit. Make sure to not let the measuring tape go and make sure you start from the 0 mark on the tape!</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-62578a9f"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-a30ac25d">Mark with a pencil, or remember the number that meets up with your starting point at 0. Note how many millimeters or centimaters it took to wrap the measure tape around your finger.</span></li><li data-pf-type="List.Item" class="sc-oUnPI iVVzrr pf-8a9f2346"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-82a4fc48">Match your finger measuremnt (in mm) with the corresponding ring size in the ring chart shown in method #02. If your tape is only showing in centimeter, use an online CM to MM converter to figure out your finger size in the closest millimeter.</span></li></ul></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-fc48ce7a" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-dbc4296a"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-51c07eea pf-r pf-r-align--cm" style="--pf-s-lg:0px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-1ee551c0" data-pf-type="Column"><h6 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-da021ee5"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3dabda02">tips & tricks</span></h6></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Divider" class="sc-qQKeD hpksip pf-a07c4f6f"><div></div></div><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-923872c1 pf-r pf-r-align--ct" style="--pf-s-lg:16px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--3 pf-c-md--3 pf-c-lg--3"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-5028b33a" data-pf-type="Column"></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--6 pf-c-md--6 pf-c-lg--6"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-730b9238" data-pf-type="Column"><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-2ed2730b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-227dbdd9">The weather can effect your finger size. During the cold weather your fingers can shrink up to half a size, while when it's too hot your fingers expands more. Make sure to measure your fingers are at room temperature to get a more accurate reading.
Avoid measuring your fingers after you had some salty snacks and a couple of glasses of wine because alcohol and salt can make your fingers swell!
If you're between sizes, we recommend ordring up. It's always easier to size a ring smaller, than larger.
